3. Great new Visual Studio Net8.0 MSTest (Microsoft's built-in framework)
4. Down laod the UnitTest cases as provided
5. Adapt the supplied code to your local MSTest envionment. including configuration of your DeviceToken pathway.
6. Execute the supplied UnitTest cases to verify correct operation of the code funtionality.

